guage=EN>Daeanor Endarion</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/picon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/22/02 2:52:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/ppic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SoTF- Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> You are in the right places, just bad luck. The ledge just before the King Room (before giants) is often a good spot. <p><table width = 30%><tr><td align=center style=filter:glow(color=#cc0000 strength=1)><font size=2 color=#ffff00 face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Daeanor Endarion of the Rathe</font></td></tr><tr><td align=center><font size = -1><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=23437>~ <i>profile</i> ~</a></font></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unileyanightwish.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nileya Nightwish</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://wmstoyz.homestead.com/files/graphics/changeheart.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/22/02 11:11:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://wmstoyz.homestead.com/files/graphics/yen6.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SoTF- Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> got mine yesterday from a wizard in the middle room of the jail hallway. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uhibashira.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hibashira</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/22/02 11:22:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SoTF- Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> Got mine by the first gate (2 gates before the King Room).  3 mobs.  A light blue ice goblin wizard gave me the heart.  You probably just had a bad run. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyahtzooba.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yahtzooba</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/22/02 8:27:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SoTF- Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> You are in the right places, just a bad string. I had popped several dozen before a shaman had one drop that he let me loot. Give a /shout out to other hunters - just might help.<br><br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://208.57.3.217/yaht/Boom41.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugarrathmoore.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Garrath Moore</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/12/02 7:18:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SoTF- Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> I got lucky on that one. First wizard I dropped, had it. Heart of Fire took me forever. I think I killed 2 dozen inferno gob wiz's before I got one :/ <p>Garrath Moore <BR>Wizard of the 54th Norrath Shattering Kaboom!<BR>Officer, Divine Fate <BR>Ayonae Ro <BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=313465"> View Me </A>   </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugarielhalliwell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gariel Halliwell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/13/02 8:11:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SoTF- Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> I had the same thing happen to me Garrath.  The heart of fire took me several trips to get but first goblin I killed in Permafrost dropped the heart.<br><br>Sounds like you are just unlucky with the drops.  Keep at it, the staff is well worth the effort.<br><br>Mistress Gariel Halliwell<br>Sorcerer of The Hand, Xev <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umernixmarrson.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mernix Marrson</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/18/02 12:35:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SoTF- Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> Got Heart of Frost within 10 mins of entering Permafrost. I remember where it was but I don't know the name for it. Sorry. But definitely not anywhere near the entrance with Ice Giants i.e not anywhere near the King.<br><br>Now for Heart of Fire, after spending like about 2 hours, somehow told me there was one that just dropped. It was at the pit.<br><br>Later, in a group, we actually had TWO of them dropped in the bar. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utulinx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>tulinx</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/21/02 2:23:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.malignwarlock.com/pics/mw/mw.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SoTF- Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> 4 hours. killed &lt;thinks&gt; about 1200 gobbies... no heart. &lt;sigh&gt; <p><hr><p align="center"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=270100"><img border="0" src="http://www.malignwarlock.com/eq/tulinxbamsig.jpg" width="500" height="75" alt='magelo profile'></a></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uhibashira.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hibashira</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/21/02 3:52:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SoTF- Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> Only the wiards drop the heart. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uusrbinperldashw.showPublicProfile?language=EN>usrbinperl dashw</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/22/02 6:24:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~chort/images/doin-tux.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SoTF- Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> Only the Inferno Wizards, to be specific.  Most of the pop in the bar area. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ukaroluseq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KarolusEQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/23/02 1:55:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> An observation on the Hearts</span><hr size=1> Well met,<br><br>Just thought I wanted to share this one with people who are after the Hearts: We did the hunt yesterday and I guess I have to consider myself damn lucky - Heart of Fire dropped off the first inferno wizard I nuked into oblivion and the second wizard in Perma lost his heart to me as well. Now here is where I found them:<br><br>Fire - In one of the small rooms south of the bar (the left one, to be exactly). Only one mob in there. Someone else in this thread found his there too, so this might be a good place to hang out and clear. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I do not know what mob the wizard is sharing his spawn point with (I did not stay around).<br><br>Frost - Middle cell in the Jail corridor. Again, someone else in this thread found his there. It is the cell where the Icy Goblin spawns (4 in there). We cleared it once and the next repop brought a wizard. Now it MIGHT be possible that this wizard is sharing the spawn point with the Icy Goblin (who was only there initially but not on the repop) but it is hard to tell since there are two mobs standing very close together.<br><br>Hope this helps a bit. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Take care, <br><br>Etidure <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/upaennewizard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Paenne Wizard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/24/02 1:07:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: An observation on the Hearts</span><hr size=1> The best place I think is the area of the jial.  There are two places a wizard spawns, one is in the room where the barrels are the other is in the middle room on the right hand side of the jail hallway.  I got my heart in there and so did the two wizzy ahead of me who gave me the area to camp.  I just killed everything in that area.  Would walk into a room and PBAoE it and kill all the mobs and then loot and move on.  Took me about 90 minutes or so. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utholien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tholien</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/24/02 9:14:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: An observation on the Hearts</span><hr size=1> I found mine in a room with a big rune on the floor and a frozen goblin king in a chunk of ice.  There were two ice goblin wizards in there and the second one I killed had the heart.  The heart from SolA took me about 5 inferno goblin wizard kills to finnally get.<br><br>Kysos Stinger 51 lvl Wizard Xev<br>Honored Circle <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=585.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=585.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=585.topic&index=13><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=585.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.threadControl?topicID=585.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=585.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=585.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td